56
00:05:06,054 --> 00:05:08,154
Kita sudah makan mochi.

57
00:05:08,154 --> 00:05:09,654
Apa kau masih tidur?

58
00:05:09,654 --> 00:05:11,554
Demam, aku demam.

59
00:05:11,554 --> 00:05:13,854
Yah, aku hanya batuk sedikit,

60
00:05:13,854 --> 00:05:15,954
