67
00:05:31,554 --> 00:05:34,054
Bukankah itu infeksi saluran pernafasan atas yang akut?

68
00:05:34,054 --> 00:05:36,154
Apa?

69
00:05:36,154 --> 00:05:37,354
Bodoh.

70
00:05:37,354 --> 00:05:38,954
"Infeksi saluran pernapasan atas akut"

71
00:05:38,954 --> 00:05:40,354
